  "fullArabic": "يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوٓاْ أَطِيعُواْ ٱللَّهَ وَأَطِيعُواْ ٱلرَّسُولَ وَأُوْلِي ٱلۡأَمۡرِ مِنكُمۡۖ فَإِن تَنَٰزَعۡتُمۡ فِي شَيۡءٖ فَرُدُّوهُ إِلَى ٱللَّهِ وَٱلرَّسُولِ إِن كُنتُمۡ تُؤۡمِنُونَ بِٱللَّهِ وَٱلۡيَوۡمِ ٱلۡأٓخِرِۚ ذَٰلِكَ خَيۡرٞ وَأَحۡسَنُ تَأۡوِيلًا",
  "fullTranslation": "O you who have believed, obey Allah and obey the Messenger and those in authority among you. And if you disagree over anything, refer it to Allah and the Messenger, if you should believe in Allah and the Last Day. That is the best [way] and best in result.",
  "fullTransliteration": "yaayyuha alladhina amanu ati'u al-laha wa-ati'u al-rasula wa-uli al-amri minkum fa-in tanaza'tum fi shayin farudduhu ila al-lahi wal-rasuli in kuntum tu'minuna bil-lahi wal-yawmi al-akhiri dhalika khayrun wa-ahsanu tawilan"
